cc:Work.dc:title: Yamanote Train
cc:Work.dc:description: Nothing says "Tokyo" more than the Yamanote line. It cuts through the heart of downtown, carrying millions of passengers a day. I didn't see any clipart on here, and so I cooked up something myself. I'm not the best artist, but I hope this helps someone who needs clipart of a Japanese train. Hey maybe for a presentation about Japan for your class? Or maybe for your Train Lovers Group that meets on every Monday to eat meat and talk about trains? No? What?
